# vastai_overlay_member (Resource)

Joins an instance to a Vast.ai overlay network. Uses a composite ID format of `overlay_id/instance_id`. **Note:** Individual instance removal from an overlay is not supported by the API. Destroying this resource removes it from Terraform state only.

